         Yes, don't hunt for CHA items.  I really thing we need a banner that says "CHARM, MEZ, AND FEAR FOR NECROS DOESN'T CHANGE DUE TO CHA".   Fear is unaffected by CHA, positive or negative, and charm/mez is only very, very, very slightly effected by CHA for necros.  Different tables from the Enchanters.  </P><P>For selling I use a pair of Opal Encrusted Steins to boost me to 107 CHA, which is 3 shy of the maximum (you get no further price change from 110 CHA on).  If they're all I need, you should be fine.</P><P><i><b><font color=gold><font size=4>Dinomight Questaholic</b></font id=size4><BR>Master of the Lizard Dance on Test  {The Grove}</i></font id=gold><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
